CVE-2026-31802
# CVE-2024-21538: cross-spawn (npm) ReDoS
# False positive: python:3.14-slim has no Node.js/npm runtime; no package.json in image
# Trivy attributing npm CVE from GitHub Actions runner environment
# Accepted: 2026-07-04, Owner: Jonas (Engineering), Ref: HBE-1768
CVE-2024-21538
# CVE-2026-59873/59874: tar (npm) DoS via gzip bomb / malformed tar header
