# runtime and no npm packages in the container image; tar npm package not present.
# Accepted: 2026-07-22, Owner: Jonas (Engineering), Ref: HBE-2400
CVE-2026-59873
CVE-2026-59874
# CVE-2026-13149: brace-expansion (npm) DoS via exponential-time O(2^n) expansion
# False positive: same runner-attribution pattern — mein-assistent is a pure Python/Streamlit app
# with no Node.js runtime, no npm, no package.json in the container image. Trivy picks up
# brace-expansion from the GitHub Actions runner environment, not from the container image.
